{"code":200,"message":"OK","tweet":{"url":"https://x.com/alexmashrabov/status/1998688373804790147","id":"1998688373804790147","text":"AI-native companies have more agility to grow to $1T at 70% margin than incumbents reinventing themselves","raw_text":{"text":"AI-native companies have more agility to grow to $1T at 70% margin than incumbents reinventing themselves","display_text_range":[0,105],"facets":[]},"author":{"screen_name":"alexmashrabov","url":"https://x.com/alexmashrabov","id":"1570599115","followers":12406,"following":306,"likes":2044,"media_count":31,"name":"Alex 🧩 Scaling Video GenAI","description":"CEO at @higgsfield. Best video GenAI for social media. cofounder at AI Factory (acq by Snap)","raw_description":{"text":"CEO at @higgsfield. Best video GenAI for social media. cofounder at AI Factory (acq by Snap)","facets":[]},"location":"San Francisco","banner_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1570599115/1770829252","avatar_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2045602055604322304/-BLI5cZM_200x200.jpg","joined":"Fri Jul 05 13:56:05 +0000 2013","protected":false,"website":{"url":"http://higgsfield.ai","display_url":"higgsfield.ai"},"verification":{"verified":true,"verified_at":null,"type":"individual"},"avatar_color":null},"replies":5,"retweets":2,"likes":28,"bookmarks":6,"quotes":0,"created_at":"Wed Dec 10 09:36:56 +0000 2025","created_timestamp":1765359416,"views":4015,"is_note_tweet":false,"community_note":null,"lang":"en","replying_to":null,"replying_to_status":null,"quote":{"url":"https://x.com/patrick_oshag/status/1998486860604256333","id":"1998486860604256333","text":"Gavin on why it's a mistake for SaaS companies to resist AI because it has a lower margin structure:\n\n\"When there's a transformative new technology customers are demanding, it's always a mistake not to embrace it.\n\nIf you're trying to preserve an 80% gross-margin structure, you are guaranteed not to succeed in AI.\n\nSaaS companies are making the exact same mistake that brick and mortar retailers did with e-commerce. They clearly saw customer demand, but they didn't like the margin structure. Now Amazon has higher margins -- margins can change. \n\nSaaS companies have their 70-90% gross margins and are reluctant to accept AI gross margins -- a good AI company might have 40%.\n\nIf you want to have an agent, it's never going to succeed if you're not willing to run it at a sub-35% gross margin because that's what the AI natives are running it at.\n\nI can't think of a single application SaaS company that could not be running a successful agent strategy. And they have a giant advantage over these AI natives in that they have a cash-generative business.\"","raw_text":{"text":"Gavin on why it's a mistake for SaaS companies to resist AI because it has a lower margin structure:\n\n\"When there's a transformative new technology customers are demanding, it's always a mistake not to embrace it.\n\nIf you're trying to preserve an 80% gross-margin structure, you are guaranteed not to succeed in AI.\n\nSaaS companies are making the exact same mistake that brick and mortar retailers did with e-commerce. They clearly saw customer demand, but they didn't like the margin structure. Now Amazon has higher margins -- margins can change. \n\nSaaS companies have their 70-90% gross margins and are reluctant to accept AI gross margins -- a good AI company might have 40%.\n\nIf you want to have an agent, it's never going to succeed if you're not willing to run it at a sub-35% gross margin because that's what the AI natives are running it at.\n\nI can't think of a single application SaaS company that could not be running a successful agent strategy. And they have a giant advantage over these AI natives in that they have a cash-generative business.\"","display_text_range":[0,1058],"facets":[{"type":"media","indices":[279,302],"id":"1998476628783992832","display":"pic.x.com/5ICqTaHbDW","original":"https://t.co/5ICqTaHbDW","replacement":"https://x.com/patrick_oshag/status/1998486860604256333/video/1"}]},"author":{"screen_name":"patrick_oshag","url":"https://x.com/patrick_oshag","id":"1528558014","followers":343404,"following":2475,"likes":40878,"media_count":2939,"name":"Patrick OShaughnessy","description":"building @psumvc @colossusmag hosting @investlikebest","raw_description":{"text":"building @psumvc @colossusmag hosting @investlikebest","facets":[]},"location":"New York, NY","banner_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1528558014/1745788104","avatar_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1964115465065664512/ZFQbGjIU_200x200.jpg","joined":"Tue Jun 18 19:06:20 +0000 2013","protected":false,"website":{"url":"https://colossus.com/subscribe","display_url":"colossus.com/subscribe"},"verification":{"verified":true,"verified_at":null,"type":"individual"},"avatar_color":null},"replies":24,"retweets":42,"likes":443,"bookmarks":235,"quotes":11,"created_at":"Tue Dec 09 20:16:12 +0000 2025","created_timestamp":1765311372,"possibly_sensitive":false,"views":88078,"is_note_tweet":true,"community_note":null,"lang":"en","replying_to":null,"replying_to_status":null,"media":{"all":[{"id":"1998476628783992832","url":"https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1998476628783992832/vid/avc1/1080x1080/VrfYVNp_4EBLIn0y.mp4?tag=21","thumbnail_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/1998476628783992832/img/PVvYINkwhRSFTCUf.jpg","duration":175.141,"width":1080,"height":1080,"format":"video/mp4","type":"video","formats":[{"url":"https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1998476628783992832/pl/Dci_8K7OV-DymMLM.m3u8?tag=21&v=884","container":"m3u8"},{"url":"https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1998476628783992832/vid/avc1/320x320/9PLz14Q9VmxGfPTV.mp4?tag=21","bitrate":432000,"container":"mp4","codec":"h264"},{"url":"https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1998476628783992832/vid/avc1/540x540/d2LxKXF05CDor0l7.mp4?tag=21","bitrate":832000,"container":"mp4","codec":"h264"},{"url":"https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/1998476628783992832/